have a question or two, below.

On Mon, 9 Sep 2019 at 12:40, Eric W. Biederman <ebiederm@xmission.com> wrote:
>
> "Michael Kerrisk (man-pages)" <mtk.manpages@gmail.com> writes:
>
> > Hello Philipp,
